Package com.lukeleber.scandroid.sae

Implementations of various related ISO/SAE standards can be found within this package.

See: Description

Package com.lukeleber.scandroid.sae Description

Implementations of various related ISO/SAE standards can be found within this package. Each implementation resides in its own "sub-package" and exists somewhat independently except for occasions where various standards explicitly link and/or refer to each other. For example, SAE J1979 (Diagnostic Test Modes) refers to SAE J2012 (Diagnostic Trouble Codes) such that DTCs defined by J2012 are included in J1979.
